# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
#
# Intentionally empty.
#
# LaserForge has no client-side routes, so a catch-all SPA rewrite is
# unnecessary. More importantly, rewriting missing `/assets/*.js` chunks to
# `index.html` breaks module workers: a stale tab can request an old hashed
# trace-worker chunk and receive HTML with a 200 instead of a real asset miss.
